Package booking

Class Booking

java.lang.Object
booking.Booking
public class Booking extends Object
Class that represents a booking. This class encapsulates the details of a booking including the booking ID, customer ID, customer name, concert ID, total number of tickets, and the list of ticket details. author Yoshikazu Fujisaka
